snippet.textDisplay: Just amazing!!!....  I am a singing-loving person, that's why I listen to all kinds of songs, language is not a bar for me. Though I am Bengali I understand Odia a little bit, because a friend from Balasore and I visited Puri 6th time. So she suggested to me some Odia songs! and among all this is one of the sweetest compositions. Especially the "Bande Utkal Janani" ..line just touch my heart. I really got emotional. Thank you for this composition. Lots of love from Kolkata.
snippet.textOriginal: Just amazing!!!....  I am a singing-loving person, that's why I listen to all kinds of songs, language is not a bar for me. Though I am Bengali I understand Odia a little bit, because a friend from Balasore and I visited Puri 6th time. So she suggested to me some Odia songs! and among all this is one of the sweetest compositions. Especially the "Bande Utkal Janani" ..line just touch my heart. I really got emotional. Thank you for this composition. Lots of love from Kolkata.
